metadata.description: Travel itinerary with dates and addresses for stops in Yokohama, Manila, Singapore, Calcutta, Bombay, Cairo, Naples, and Italy.
metadata.transcript:
Upham Itinerary Address Mailing dates

from Oxford, Ohio

Yokohama and Japan December 6 - 19 American Express Co. 7 Nihon Odori, Nakaku (P. O. Box 407) Yokohama, Japan November 17 - 24

Manila December 27 - January 5 American Express Co. 95 Plaza Moraga (P. O. Box 1463) Manila, P. I. November 24 - December 1

Singapore January 9 - 27 American Express Co. No. 1, Collyer Quay Singapore, Straits Settlements December 1 - 14

Calcutta February 6 - 7 American Express Co. 14-15 Government Place, East (P. O. Box 2331) Calcutta, India December 14 - January 1

Bombay February 17 - 18 American Express Co. 82-84 Esplanade Road, Fort (P. O. Box 507) Bombay, India January 1 - 21

Cairo February 28 - March 14 American Express Co. Continental Savoy Bldg. (P. O. Box 2160) Cairo, Egypt January 21 - February 28

Naples and Italy March 19 - April 10 American Express Co. 23a Piazza dei Martiri Naples, Italy February 28 - March 15 American Express Co. Via Balbi (Hotel Colombia) Genoa, Italy March 15 - 30
